Absolutely! Here's how to enhance your Dashboard so that:

âœ… The comment is shown in the table for each task.

âœ… Users can filter tasks by keyword (in any field including comment, status, file names, etc.)

âœ… 1. Update the Dashboard Table to Include Comments
In dashboard.html:
A. Add a new <th> for the Comment:
html
Copy
Edit
<th>Comment</th>
B. Add a new <td> in the row for each task:
